com.ikalagaming.event

Annotation Type EventHandler


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface EventHandler
    An annotation to mark methods as being event handler methods. Based off lahwran's fevents.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      Order order
      Define the order of the event handler relative to the default.

    • Element Detail

      • order

        public abstract Order order
        Define the order of the event handler relative to the default.

        Order of execution from first to last:

        1. EARLIEST
        2. EARLY
        3. DEFAULT
        4. LATE
        5. LATEST
        6. MONITOR
        Returns:
        Returns this handler's priority
        Default:
        com.ikalagaming.event.Order.DEFAULT
